summaries.short: Series premiere. Detective Angela Abar and Chief Judd Crawford investigate the attempted murder of a cop.
summaries.full: Series premiere. In an alternate America where police conceal their identities behind masks to protect themselves from a terrorist organization, Detective Angela Abar investigates the attempted murder of a fellow officer under the guidance of her friend and Chief, Judd Crawford. Meanwhile, the Lord of a Country Estate receives an anniversary gift from his loyal servants.
